He's a specialist
that hides his money.

480
00:21:01.696 --> 00:21:03.330
<i>He bounces it around</i>
<i>between countries</i>

481
00:21:03.463 --> 00:21:05.800
<i>and buries it under layers</i>
<i>of shell companies</i>

482
00:21:06.033 --> 00:21:08.236
