501
00:21:49.811 --> 00:21:52.345
<i>You got an invite to his party</i>
<i>as a potential investor.</i>

502
00:21:52.814 --> 00:21:54.447
<i>To catch his attention.</i>
<i>you need to win.</i>

503
00:21:54.615 --> 00:21:56.651
