and efficiently as possible.

694
00:28:34.381 --> 00:28:36.050
We're gonna be ready
for any eventuality

695
00:28:36.183 --> 00:28:37.484
and practice until
we get it right.

696
00:28:37.652 --> 00:28:41.355
But this is Salazar's Island.

697
00:28:41.488 --> 00:28:43.224
